---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Risk Management: Safeguard Your Bets and Maximize Wins" description="Discover essential risk management strategies for smart betting in casinos and sports. Learn to protect your bankroll, set limits, and bet with confidence at BetSmart Academy.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-900 via-purple-900 to-indigo-900"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,')] opacity-10"></div>
    
    <div class="relative container mx-auto px-4 py-24 md:py-32 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
        <span class="bg-amber-500 text-gray-900 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Strategy</span>
        <span class="mx-3 text-white">•</span>
        <span class="bg-red-500 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">Risk Control</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 max-w-3xl leading-tight">
        Risk Management: Safeguard Your Bets and Maximize Wins
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 max-w-2xl mb-10">
        Master smart betting strategies for casino and sports. Protect your bankroll and bet with confidence at BetSmart Academy.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          Start Learning
        </button>
        <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-indigo-900 transition-all duration-300">
          Watch Demo
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Risk Management Matters -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-900 to-gray-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Master Risk Management: Bet Smarter, Not Harder!
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-purple-100 mb-16">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          In the high-stakes world of casino games and sports betting, <strong>risk management</strong> isn't just a buzzword—it's your ultimate shield against devastating losses and the key to long-term success. At BetSmart Academy, we empower you to <strong>master smart betting strategies</strong> that keep the thrill alive without the financial heartache. Ready to level up? Let's dive in!
        </p>
        
        <div class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-700 to-indigo-800 rounded-xl p-6 border border-purple-600 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-xl font-bold text-white">
            <i class="fas fa-star text-yellow-400 mr-2"></i>
            At BetSmart Academy, we turn betting into a strategic art form
            <i class="fas fa-star text-yellow-400 ml-2"></i>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-800 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-6 text-red-500">
            <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Preserve Your Bankroll</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-200">
            Ensure you have funds for future bets, not just one big gamble. Smart allocation keeps you in the game longer.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-800 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-6 text-red-500">
            <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Make Informed Decisions</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-200">
            Avoid emotional bets driven by hype or frustration. Use data-driven strategies to guide your choices.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800 to-gray-900 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-800 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-6 text-red-500">
            <i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Sustain the Fun</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-200">
            Turn betting into a sustainable hobby that brings joy, not stress. Enjoy the thrill responsibly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Risk Management Strategies -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-900 to-indigo-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Essential Risk Management Strategies</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-purple-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Learn how to implement proven techniques for better betting outcomes
        </p>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900 to-indigo-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-700 hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl text-red-500 mr-4 mt-1">
                  <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Set Bankroll Limits</h3>
                  <p class="text-purple-200">
                    Never risk more than 1-5% of your total bankroll on a single bet. This approach protects you from catastrophic losses while allowing for growth.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900 to-indigo-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-700 hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl text-red-500 mr-4 mt-1">
                  <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Use Risk-to-Reward Ratios</h3>
                  <p class="text-purple-200">
                    Ensure your potential reward justifies the risk. A 1:2 risk-reward ratio means you could lose 100 but win 200 - that's a smart move.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900 to-indigo-900 p-6 rounded-xl border border-purple-700 hover:border-purple-500 transition-all duration-300">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl text-red-500 mr-4 mt-1">
                  <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Time Your Bets Wisely</h3>
                  <p class="text-purple-200">
                    Avoid betting when emotions run high. Take time to assess situations calmly, especially with sports betting where conditions can change rapidly.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-orange-500 rounded-2xl p-8 transform rotate-3 shadow-2xl">
            <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-700">
              <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
                <div class="text-white">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-xl">Smart Betting Calculator</h4>
                  <p class="text-purple-300">Risk Management Tool</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-2xl text-yellow-300">
                  <i class="fas fa-calculator"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <label class="text-purple-200 text-sm">Bankroll Amount</label>
                  <div class="relative">
                    <input type="text" value="$1,000" class="w-full bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 border border-gray-700 focus:border-purple-500 focus:outline-none">
                    <span class="absolute right-3 top-3 text-purple-300">$</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                  <label class="text-purple-200 text-sm">Bet Size</label>
                  <div class="relative">
                    <input type="text" value="$50" class="w-full bg-gray-800 text-white rounded-lg px-4 py-3 border border-gray-700 focus:border-purple-500 focus:outline-none">
                    <span class="absolute right-3 top-3 text-purple-300">$</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                  <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="text-purple-300 text-sm">Risk Level</p>
                    <p class="text-white font-bold">5%</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <p class="text-purple-300 text-sm">Success Rate</p>
                    <p class="text-white font-bold">68%</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-indigo-600 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded-lg hover:from-purple-700 hover:to-indigo-700 transition-all duration-300">
                  Calculate Strategy
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full opacity-30 animate-ping"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-900 via-purple-900 to-indigo-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Ready to Take Control of Your Betting?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Join thousands of smart bettors who've transformed their approach with our proven risk management strategies.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
          <button class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transform hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 text-lg">
            Start Your Risk Management Journey
          </button>
          <button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-indigo-900 transition-all duration-300 text-lg">
            View Free Resources
          </button>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="text-3xl text-red-500 mr-3">
              <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white text-lg">50,000+ Active Members</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="text-3xl text-red-500 mr-3">
              <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white text-lg">100% Success Rate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="text-3xl text-red-500 mr-3">
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white text-lg">4.9/5 Rating</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>